RESIGNATION OF AN OFFICER OF A CORPORATION


RESIGNATION


TO:		[NAME OF CORPORATION]

AND TO:	THE DIRECTORS THEREOF




I HEREBY tender my resignation as [CAPACITY IN WHICH RESIGNATION IS BEING MADE (ie. President, Vice-President, Secretary, Treasurer, etc...)] of the Corporation to take effect forthwith.

DATED: [EFFECTIVE DATE OF RESIGNATION, ex. July 1, 1998]




…………………………………………..
[NAME OF PERSON RESIGNING]
